*********************************************
Python for Process Engineering Schema (PyPES)
*********************************************

.. image::
   https://github.com/we3lab/pype-schema/workflows/Build%20Main/badge.svg
   :height: 30
   :target: https://github.com/we3lab/pype-schema/actions
